channel.title: How do I use hamachi?
channel.description:
hello, I have downloaded hamachi and i have it joined to a server, I have a list of the people in the server at the moment and it says it is online. When I write the IP it tells you to put in, it does not work.
I click the join existing network button,and i put in the name and pass and from there i do not understand why cannot get on (i have never used hamachi before)
what am i doing wrong?? [br][size=1]Posted on: March 04, 2007, 11:09:06 AM[/size][hr].
